    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape! It runs like a dream, the interior is nice and clean, and it\u2019s definitely been well-loved over the years. If you're looking for a dependable daily driver that's ready to hit the road today, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
