    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that perfectly balances performance and comfort. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish that shines beautifully in the sunlight, though a discerning eye might find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper\u2014honest signs of its time on the open road. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple and free of tears, and every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system, operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with a recent full inspection and oil service completed just last month. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the engine provides smooth, responsive power. With tires that offer ample tread and a clean, non-smoker interior, this car is ready for its next chapter. It is an ideal choice for a buyer seeking a reliable, high-quality vehicle that has been treated with genuine care.",
      "price": 34500.0,
