    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it\u2019s ready for its next adventure right away. Everything runs smoothly, the interior is super comfy, and it still looks great parked in the driveway. It's the perfect dependable car for someone who wants quality without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
