    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This A80 Supra Turbo is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE sequential twin-turbocharged inline-six. The powertrain remains mechanically robust, paired with the factory-correct Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox and a Torsen limited-slip differential. The forced induction system maintains consistent peak boost, while the double-wishbone suspension geometry ensures precise handling characteristics. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive fluid flush and timing belt replacement to ensure the structural and mechanical integrity of the platform. While the exterior shows the honest patina of a well-loved performance machine, the drivetrain remains tight with excellent compression and synchro engagement. It is a turn-key enthusiast's car ready for the street or further tuning.",
